    Black Aracnia has enough of this. She is now the Predacon Commander and 
orders had to be given. She looked to her group in the back.
    "Thunder Hammer, and Quickstrike, go outside and help take care of the 
Dinobots. Darkmouse and Paralysis start the manual weponry and try to scare 
off the Maximals, if not killing them. As for Rampage and the Terricons, you 
can go outside and help or get off my bridge!" She yelled, taking the command 
chair.
    Now in control, Black Aracnia took the floating keyboard and began to 
start up the old rusty missle turrets. Paralysis climed into a small cockpit 
shape chaber with two large canon that he could use to blast away anyone 
outside the ship. He targeted the Dinobots and fired.
    Aracnia typed in the sccess codes and off whissed three heat seeking 
missles, intent on making that body heat dead cold.
